GLesmos Roadmap 2023, proposed by Fasteroid.

Required:

    Outlines:
        Fix whole screen filling when no outlines are visible [ ]
        Don't run the shader if they're disabled              [ ]

    Fill:
        Implement [ ]


Desired:

    General Performance:
        Use less division in the fragment shaders  [ ]
        Use uniforms for colors, alpha, and width  [ ]
        Combine "fill" and "cache" passes          [ ]

    Outlines:
        Investigate blobby lines bug [ ]
        FIX blobby lines bug         [ ]


Future:

    Implement integrals [ ]

    Optimize sliders by passing values via uniforms [ ]

    GLesmos polygon renderer [ ]